      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by my doctor like 3 days ago here in sydney. the cut looks a bit red and feels kind of warm to the touch and there is some yellow stuff oozing out a little bit. is that normal or should i be worried? can i just put a warm compress on it and some cream from the chemist to keep it clean?",
